{
  "stem": "19550.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a guard to every train, to every cattle car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was standing below.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had just enough of a slit in the, in the one window that you usually have on these cattle cars, which by the way, was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] boarded up.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had broken it out so we could get a little bit of air.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Other than that, there was no air at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I spoke to the, to this SS man and handed him some rings and some money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we got [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the car opened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went down to get some water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then it seems to me that it must have been that he had either decided on his own or they were going to do it anyway, some of the other cars were also opened.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And like myself, some of the younger people jumped out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was, you know, water for the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we collected some water in whatever dishes and pails we-- people had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and emptied out some of the pails that we used for-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the car-- for voiding, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which, which, you know, was also, I presume, happened in every car.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But it was a spontaneous idea of one of us, cause there was no, there were no facilities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we got a little water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember I had already taken off my shirt, and I let the water run all over me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we had a little water for each of the cars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Probably lasted 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
